{"tid":2153812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【白俄警暴】不論背景 要為所有警暴受害者發聲","createTime":"2020-08-12T18:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T19:11:56.000Z","uid":84408,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b8856200b33adb8cbec025758a16ccec6d616456","tid":2153812,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"我地唔係白左<br />\n所有人嘅live 都matter <br />\n<br />\n為民主同公義嘅所有人都唔應該受迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16be756b7ff12e1323e4ae2ca64ec2596eea15a","tid":2153812,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a26e6ef09b511520a0cb4736c2cc4d6b0896816","tid":2153812,"uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"🇧🇾白俄羅斯自選舉後晚晚都如人間煉獄<br />\n現分享其中兩宗在於11/8/2020晚的警暴事件<br />\n<br />\n1）的士司機Baranovichi因政府斷網無法得知新的封路規定。於是如常工作，接載了三名乘客（約15-16歲），行駛好一會，看到交通警在前方封路。他跟排在他前面的四輛私家車停下之際，後面突然衝出一輛警車。<br />\n<br />\n防暴把車上（包括排在事主的士前的四部車）所有人拖出，把他們面朝地壓在地上，每人被四至五名防暴以警棍毆打。<br />\n其中一名年輕乘客被打至腎臟爆裂，他痛苦大叫，及後更開始口吐白沫。<br />\n<br />\n接著防暴用警棍把車輛打爛。幾乎把所有人帶上警車，只留下青年及Baranovichi。臨行前更有警察語跟他說：「你可以繼續工作了。」<br />\n<br />\n2）同一晚，在薄餅店Domino's Pizza也上演相似的一幕。防暴衝進Domino搜查。要全餐廳的顧客跟工作人員&ldquo;面朝下躺在地板上&rdquo;。查問及搜查各人隨身物品後才離開。<br />\n 離開時警車更撞上了一輛Domino的汽車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLzbg4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLzbg4r.jpg&h=3854b2b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvpVJKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvpVJKs.jpg&h=d558b0a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBJjqXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBJjqXO.jpg&h=1ab5e743&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi