gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd05c39581706b717cb9df491c4ba34cee205c1","tid":2153812,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"人地白俄鎮壓有咩問題"},{"pid":"b290e2453eb1ddfea9dd393d9004f74ffd457974","tid":2153812,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:35:13.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fb339283054d0639598e2a87a84139b3c61170","tid":2153812,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"c12d8be34d30ecc2932e8bdaa47e9d924663881c","tid":2153812,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"推!!! Stand with Belarus !!!!!!"},{"pid":"71a15de6bb590ff481d496a0590eaf3ffb50279c","tid":2153812,"uid":283764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:40:42.000Z","msg":"Stand with Belarus"},{"pid":"ed2ad220ed174ecb474787f93ebac61076f9e708","tid":2153812,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"#standwithBelarus<br />\n<br />\n#LukashenkoLeaveNow"},{"pid":"8537ae142a86c2fb3db3e7b61ec9a3fa92f8470c","tid":2153812,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"08a471d283cacfd6ea8d229a41b39915d3263381","tid":2153812,"uid":279606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"Stand with Belarus"},{"pid":"01dae0acf4a39f9f0527e7275cff713a91222f5b","tid":2153812,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017e3b7e942771e6a8726d2091b0e9bd23212ab3","tid":2153812,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03566af141ce18933d8caecfadaa55eb27661f4","tid":2153812,"uid":77355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bd05c39581706b717cb9df491c4ba34cee205c1","tid":2153812,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"人地白俄鎮壓有咩問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"會員 #165028 - 何東精神（團結）<br />\n，前稱純正港人(港豬)，離地中產，天安門旅遊，Frizzle(港豬)，Alexander(離地)極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍, 請大家多加注意!<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n#1 - 周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢<br />\n<br />\n#1 - 誠哥真係好醒目<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 好怕d勇武派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車<br />\n<br />\n#1 - （求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 想報仇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767121</a><br />\n<br />\n[quote]發現女朋友個WhatsApp 有同第二個男仔有纏綿對話<br />\n我知道個男仔有參加社會又搞衝擊<br />\n宜家想搞佢罪証再報警篤灰"},{"pid":"aecd82f1152dca810b4930d751afc200fb655f88","tid":2153812,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"撐你既講法，但你有無支持blm先"},{"pid":"156e639f386d67697baffeab2300dbb950ac1cc7","tid":2153812,"uid":84408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aecd82f1152dca810b4930d751afc200fb655f88","tid":2153812,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"撐你既講法，但你有無支持blm先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"Blm 其實本質上係應該撐<br />\n但呢加個趨勢 已經唔係平反與訴求嘅問題 都唔知撐乜 <br />\n當然對於警暴一定係反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d8a9a5335c853b207119592271f7f90a65149e","tid":2153812,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:11:56.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}